
# Employee Attendance System ‚Äì Backend

The Employee Attendance System is a web-based platform designed to help employees record their attendance and managers track attendance records efficiently. It ensures secure authentication and stores attendance data reliably in a database.

This is the backend application built using Node.js, Express, and MongoDB, which provides APIs for authentication and attendance management.

---

üöÄ Tech Stack

- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- Mongoose
- JWT Authentication
- bcryptjs
- dotenv

---

üîê Core Modules

### 1Ô∏è‚É£ User Management Module
Handles user-related operations in the system.

- User Registration ‚Äì Allows employees and managers to create accounts.
- Password Encryption ‚Äì Secures passwords using bcrypt hashing.
- User Data Storage ‚Äì Stores user details in MongoDB.
- Role Assignment ‚Äì Assigns roles such as employee or manager.

---

### 2Ô∏è‚É£ Authentication Module
Manages secure login and identity verification.

- User Login ‚Äì Validates email and password.
- JWT Token Generation ‚Äì Creates secure tokens after successful login.
- Token Verification ‚Äì Protects private routes using middleware.
- Secure Session Handling ‚Äì Ensures authenticated API access.

---

### 3Ô∏è‚É£ Authorization Module
Controls access based on user roles.

- Role-Based Access Control ‚Äì Restricts manager-only routes.
- Protected Routes ‚Äì Ensures only authenticated users can access attendance APIs.

---

### 4Ô∏è‚É£ Attendance Management Module
Handles attendance tracking and storage.

- Check-In Functionality ‚Äì Records employee check-in time.
- Check-Out Functionality ‚Äì Records check-out time.
- Attendance Status ‚Äì Marks present, absent, or late.
- Attendance History ‚Äì Retrieves past attendance records.
- Working Hours Calculation ‚Äì Calculates total working hours.

---

### 5Ô∏è‚É£ Manager Control Module
Provides administrative capabilities.

- View All Employees Attendance
- Filter Attendance by Date or Employee
- View Team Summary
- Generate Attendance Reports

---

### 6Ô∏è‚É£ Database Module
Manages data storage and retrieval.

- MongoDB Integration
- User Collection
- Attendance Collection
- Schema Validation using Mongoose

---

### 7Ô∏è‚É£ API Module
Provides RESTful endpoints for frontend communication.

- Auth APIs (Register, Login)
- Attendance APIs (Check-in, Check-out, History)
- Manager APIs (View All, Reports)

---

### 8Ô∏è‚É£ Security & Middleware Module
Ensures application security and proper request handling.

- JWT Middleware
- Password Hashing
- Error Handling
- Environment Variable Configuration using dotenv

